Monitoring in Airflow

What is Monitoring?

Monitoring means tracking:

DAG health

task states

failures

retries

execution duration



---

Important Monitoring Areas

DAG Runs

Shows:

running DAGs

failed DAGs

successful DAGs



---

Graph View

Visual workflow execution.

Very important for debugging dependencies.


---

Gantt View

Shows task execution duration.

Used to identify:

slow tasks

bottlenecks



---

Task Duration

Helps identify:

performance problems

stuck tasks



---

Important Task States

State	Meaning

queued	waiting
running	executing
success	completed
failed	failed
up_for_retry	retry pending
skipped	branch skipped



---

Real Production Monitoring

Engineers monitor:

failed pipelines

delayed schedules

retry frequency

task duration spikes



